    # the search field.
    When I am on the homepage
    Then the page should not contain any chips
    When I visit the collection overview
    Then the page should not contain any chips
    When I visit the solution overview
    Then the page should not contain any chips
    When I visit the contact form
    Then the page should not contain any chips

